*.fbx binary
*.glb binary
*.gltf text eol=lf
*.wav binary
*.mp3 binary
*.ogg binary
*.flac binary
*.mp4 binary
*.mov binary
*.avi binary
*.zip binary
*.7z binary
*.rar binary
*.pdf binary
